There may also be paperwork or forms to fill out, hopefully not as this is not a handgun or weapon of mass destruction. I can research that if I get an offer. I am totally new to this sight and not all that familiar with their policies. If someone has any suggestions, please feel free to comment. Else, off to Cabela's I will go and get the 250 and buy something I can use from them. Scope, ammunition, powder, whatever. I am in the market for a long range rifle and a trade may work.
